song.title: SubEther Communique Part 2
song.info:
A continuation of a theme that began ten years ago: the SubEther Communique. A synth-funk /rock tune with demoscene elements. Enjoy!
No real guitarists were harmed in the recording of this song. Its a synth saw-lead sound that's run through a double-stack guitar amp simulator effect.
SoundCloud link: [url]https://soundcloud.com/eiriksson/subether-communique-part-2[/url]
